dct_description_sm: AMS 2 Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. no. 4379 United States. Army Map Service Inset map: "Trapani-Milo airfield". Intelligence information 1942/43. In upper left margin: Sicily 1:8,000. Contours (approx.) 25 m. V.I. and rock drawings. Sources: Italy 1:25,000 Instituto Geografico Militare. Sheet 297 III S.W. (1913). Italy 1:50,000 G.S.G.S. no. 4229. Sheet 248 III (1941). Intelligence information 1942/43. Air photographs have been used in the production of this plan.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
